name: NineKeyMIX7
description:
This model is a combination of NineKeyMIX5 as the foundation and Pika's New Generation v.1.0, merging the beautiful lighting and shadows of Pika's New Generation v.1.0 with the distinctive facial features and eyes of NineKeyMIX5. I hope everyone will like it.

However, in order to maintain the facial features, if you don't apply the relevant lighting tags, you won't achieve the same effect as in Pika's New Generation v.1.0.

For more examples of this model, you can check out my Twitter:NineKey
